text: Camel toe, or cameltoe, is slang for when the outline of a woman's labia majora is seen in tightly fitting clothes. The male equivalent of cameltoe is mooseknuckle or manbulge.Lemon, Alex. "Heartdusting." The Southern Review 46.1 (2010): 135. It is called a "camel toe" because of how the woman's labia outline is similar to that of a camel's toe. Camel toe happens as a result of wearing tight-fitting clothes, such as shorts, leggings or swimwear. ==References== Category:Slang Category:Clothing controversies
